BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:fO4mCB-D3Dxfr709POlxq
SUMMARY:Seattle Public Library Behind the Scenes
DTSTAMP:20260308T063047Z
DTSTART:20260311T130000Z
DESCRIPTION:Jason Davis\\\, the Greenwood Branch Adult Librarian\\\, joins 
	us to talk about all of the behind-the-scenes systems that keep Seattle’s 
	libraries running smoothly. Come learn about all the steps that occur when
	 you request a hold\\\, how interlibrary loans travel around\\\, how exten
	sive the collection really is\\\, how books are selected for different bra
	nches\\\, what’s in the special collections\\\, and more! RSVP: 206.297.08
	75\n\nhttps://www.phinneycenter.org/event/seattle-public-library-behind-th
